<p><strong>Analytics:</strong> Replenishment conversion, full-price rate, holdout incrementality. Playbook fit: Cohort by SKU category and acquisition source. Failure mode: Revenue without subscription churn context. Operator test: Finance replenishment margin monthly.</p>
