<p><strong>Scenario — Protein subscription:</strong> Suppress replenishment on subscribed SKU → skip-save separate → one-time add-on replenishment valid. Map this scenario to your vertical guide at /for if category-specific suppressions apply (Recharge tags, wholesale accounts, gift buyers).</p>
